etiapine, Prochlorperazine, Lumateperone, Cariprazine, Lurasidone, Mesoridazine, Methotrimeprazine, Pimavanserin, Clozapine, Triflupromazine, More', 'Triamcinolone, Fluocinolone acetonide, Fluocinolone acetonide, Betamethasone, Fluorometholone, Triamcinolone, Betamethasone, Deflazacort, Betamethasone', 1767369485);
